{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"f877dc1f-7958-434b-8b50-88466064b114","content":"`.testsettings` is a legacy format ignored by modern MSTest. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how each setting maps:\n\n| `.testsettings` | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout=30000` | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` |\n| Code coverage data collector | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>` |\n\nLet me create the `.runsettings` file and update your `.csproj`:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_014Rg282gRFfbrMnaWFt8ev5","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Migrating testsettings to runsettings"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01AjZoALunmombvx3AuxT9Q3","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-591f89ec93464862a9148462f16a60b4/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\" />\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-591f89ec93464862a9148462f16a60b4/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01CtFrceCFj49CRYGX6gDj4p","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-591f89ec93464862a9148462f16a60b4/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>","new_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirector